Package at.tfr.pfad.view

Class BookingBean

java.lang.Object
at.tfr.pfad.view.BaseBean<Booking>
at.tfr.pfad.view.BookingBean
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Named @ViewScoped public class BookingBean extends BaseBean<Booking> implements Serializable
Backing bean for Booking entities. This class provides CRUD functionality for all Booking entities. It focuses purely on Java EE 6 standards (e.g. @ConversationScoped for state management, PersistenceContext for persistence, CriteriaBuilder for searches) rather than introducing a CRUD framework or custom base class.
